headline: NZS Capital Q4 2024 Shareholder Letter
summary: The NZS Growth Equity strategy declined 1.09% in the fourth quarter of 2024 and returned 21.25% for the full year.

headline: U.S. Bank Earnings Poised To Rebound Even As Credit Slips
summary: Progressive and GEICO, which have delivered stellar private auto results in recent quarters, increased spending on advertising campaigns in 2024 as they pivoted from retrenchment to growth.
